        <item>
            <title>Thunderobot 獵刃 16 2024 電競筆電，高效性能 + 三風扇五熱管散熱技術 + 16 吋 240Hz 熒幕</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/thunderobot-16-20241244491/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=thunderobot-16-20241244491</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/thunderobot-16-20241244491/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[科技潮人]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 09:30:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Thunderobot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[獵刃 16 2024]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1244491</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Thunderobot 推出全新「獵刃 16 2024 」電競筆電，搭載最新 Intel Core i9-14900HX 處理器，NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4070 筆電顯示卡，16GB DDR5 RAM，1TB PCIe M.2 SSD 配置，採用 16 吋，2.5K 2560&#215;1600 解像度，240Hz 極速刷新率的 IPS 顯示面板，配備全新及強勁的三風扇五熱管散熱技術，帶來媲美桌面電腦的極速遊戲體驗。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864290-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244492" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864290-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864290-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864290-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864293.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864293-694x418.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="418" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864293-694x418.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864293.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Thunderobot 獵刃 16 2024 外觀設計延續 Thunderobot 筆電的電競風格，採用鋒利的刻線元素及機能標識，搭配 Thunderobot ARGB 燈效 Logo，盡顯 Thunderobot 獨有的電競魅力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-1-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-1-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>搭載 Intel Core i9-14900HX 處理器及 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4070 8GB GDDR6 筆電顯示卡，為用家提供出色的電腦效能及 NVIDIA 最新的 RTX 40 系列的 AI 技術。通過 Thunderobot 的 Control Center 內將系統的模式切換為「獨顯直連」— 極致的遊戲效能體驗、「混合輸出」— 效能與續航能力達至平衡、「核顯輸出」— 突出的續航能力表現。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244503" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-694x576.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="576" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-694x576.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd.jpg 1084w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244504" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-1-694x346.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="346" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-1-694x346.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Thunderobot 獵刃 16 2024 採用 16GB DDR5 5600MHz 記憶體及 1TB NVMe PCIe 4.0 M.2 固態硬碟，輕鬆滿足遊戲及日常辦公需求。同時間都提供 2 條合共最高支援 64GB DDR5 5600MHz 的槽位及 2 條支援 M.2 固態硬碟的槽位，方便自由更換及升級儲存容量。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-694x557.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="557" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-694x557.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor.jpg 1121w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244501" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor2-652x580.jpg" alt="" width="652" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor2-652x580.jpg 652w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor2.jpg 1011w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 652px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-1-658x580.jpg" alt="" width="658" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-1-658x580.jpg 658w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-1.jpg 1021w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 658px" /></a></p><p>顯示螢幕採用京東方的 16 吋 IPS 面板，搭配筆電的黃金 16：10 顯示比例、2K 2560&#215;1600 超清解像度、240Hz 極速刷新率、100% sRGB 色域及 DC 調光功能，呈現細膩、超高清、真實及流暢的視覺體驗，同時也避免長時間使用產生的眼睛疲勞。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-694x288.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="288" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-694x288.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-1-648x580.jpg" alt="" width="648" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-1-648x580.jpg 648w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-1.jpg 1005w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 648px" /></a></p><p>鍵盤採用下沉式的全尺寸的方向鍵及擁有獨立的數字鍵區，按鍵使用 1.8mm 超長鍵程、0.2T 微弧鍵帽、抗指紋圖層表面及三分區 RGB 背光燈效，同時將電源鍵獨立於鍵盤之外，避免誤觸的尷尬情況。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864326-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864326-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864326-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864326-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>底部使用大面積的散熱開孔，更有效的快速排走熱量。內部採用全新的「飍」(三風扇五熱管) 散熱技術，相交於普遍的筆電散熱設計採用雙風扇設計，Thunderobot 獵刃 16 2024 新增「Auxiliary Cooling Fan」，打造直衝式散熱模式，降低風扇噪音，提升散熱及降低內部零件的溫度。</p><p>凡於 2024 年 6 月 1 日至 2024 年 6 月 30 日，購買漢科代理之 Machenike / Thunderobot 迷你電腦或電競手提電腦，即可登記換領《Elden Ring Shadow of the Erdtree》(Steam 版) DLC 乙份。</p><p>活動詳情及登記表格：<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchv2vrmXijR_QKcQAI53GzbJRE5C7o-oqykK-GFgnWKWQbQg/viewform">https://bit.ly/June_Redeem</a></p><h2>Thunderobot 獵刃 16 (2024) 電競筆電</h2><p>詳情：<a href="https://shop.hornington.com/products/thunderobot-r16-2024">https://shop.hornington.com/products/thunderobot-r16-2024</a></p><p>售價：HK$11,999</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/thunderobot-16-20241244491/notebook/">Thunderobot 獵刃 16 2024 電競筆電，高效性能 + 三風扇五熱管散熱技術 + 16 吋 240Hz 熒幕</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
